engagementTypes.title: Training
engagementTypes.description: An engagement where the contracted speakers receive training to present pharmaceutical company content.

engagementTypes.title: Product Theatre
engagementTypes.description: A virtual engagement that connects to a virtual host engagement to view the speaker presentation.

engagementTypes.title: Out of Office
engagementTypes.description: An engagement where the speaker is presenting live to HCP attendees in an out of office (venue based) setting.

engagementTypes.title: Round Table
engagementTypes.description: An engagement where the speaker is presenting live to a small group of HCP attendees and AV is not required.

engagementTypes.title: In Office
engagementTypes.description: An engagement where the speaker is presenting live to HCP attendees in an office or out of office (venue based).

engagementTypes.title: Virtual Out Office
engagementTypes.description: An engagement where the speaker is presenting virtual to HCP attendees.
